	  <h2 style="font-style:underline;"><u>Public Relation Department (PRD)</u></h2>
     <h4>I. Objective</h4>
	<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
	MCommunicating news on events/activities by HH to the students of campus/public will ensure the benefit of HH
        </p>

     <h4>II. Functions of PRD</h4>
        <p>
1. Gathering updates/activities of HH from General Secretary<Br>
2. Publicity of activities among the students through mega awareness camp at every year.<Br>
3. Annual day organization provided within the budget.<Br>
4. Hospitality of the invitee or guest <Br>
5. Donor related matters like honorarium, search the Donner etc…<Br>
6. Press release time to time.<Br>
7. Outside charity<Br>

Joint secretory of PRD need to arrange EC meeting after consulting with general secretary for necessary approval and execution of each mention function. <Br>
	</p>
     <h4>III. Structure of Internal Care Department (PRD)</h4>
